  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to evaluate the course of patients with acute pancreatitis. Thereby we analyze
      different diagnostics and compare ultrasound, MRI and CT-scan in detection of necrotic areas
      and evaluate interventional therapy methods like percutaneous drainage techniques regarding
      the outcome. Laboratory values were assessed as well.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      For laboratory values different inflammation markers were measured and compared.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
